# Cloudflare Pages security headers.
# Served for every path. No build step or dependency involved.
#
# The CSP stays strict: every asset is self-hosted and no external origin is
# ever contacted. The site runs ONE small, same-origin, progressive-enhancement
# script — the in-site media viewer — bundled by Astro under /_astro/. Pages
# still work with scripting disabled (thumbnails remain plain links to the
# full-size files). Keep it this way: adding analytics, embeds, or CDN fonts
# would force this policy to be weakened.
#
# Notes:
# - script-src 'self' allows only the bundled same-origin viewer module. No
#   'unsafe-inline', no external script origins. The JSON-LD blocks are
#   <script type="application/ld+json"> data blocks, not executed script.
# - style-src needs 'unsafe-inline' because Astro inlines one scoped <style> per
#   page. With no JavaScript and no user-supplied content there is no realistic
#   injection vector, so CSP hashes are not worth the build complexity.
# - frame-ancestors 'none' supersedes X-Frame-Options.
# - HSTS intentionally omits `preload` — that is a hard-to-reverse commitment.

/*
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'none'; script-src 'self'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self'; font-src 'self'; base-uri 'none'; form-action 'none'; frame-ancestors 'none'; upgrade-insecure-requests
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), camera=(), microphone=(), payment=(), usb=()
  Referrer-Policy: same-origin
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff

# Draft public guides — placeholders, not finished resources. Keep them out of
# search indexes and archives so a draft is never surfaced as the real guide.
# Cloudflare applies these rules on top of the /* block above, so these paths
# still receive every security header.
#
# REMOVE both blocks below when the finished guide replaces the draft at the
# same URL. A published, indexable guide must not carry noindex — and follow the
# Cloudflare Cache Policy in CLAUDE.md when swapping the file at an existing URL.
/records/healthcare/ayushman-bharat-guide.pdf
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, noarchive

/records/financial-awareness/pmjjby-guide.pdf
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, noarchive
